{"tid":57892,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【1995年 - 乜嘢係Pentium?】","createTime":"2016-12-28T11:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T11:24:09.000Z","uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d23c4d6048ff573c888dfc3e64b74c9f9425f28e","tid":57892,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:24:09.000Z","msg":"以前Intel 嘅 CPU 形號係8088，80286，80386，80486咁排落去。80486之後唔叫80586，而係叫Pemtium。當年HD 1GB已經好夠。<br />\n<br />\n1995年最重要嘅電腦課題有兩個，一個係Windows 95 面世，啲人最初唔明個Start制有咩用；第二係一個叫&quot;Internet&quot;嘅新玩意，大部分人都未知係咩嚟，modem仍然唔係買機必需品。<br />\n<br />\n(成本復刻版東TOUCH 成160幾頁，我只係貼咗幾頁嘅部分，仲有三頁會介紹。中青年們有興趣都係整本番嚟懷緬下吧。)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNuCmpWyzbKpK2ESmQez1C3jMRb98Yn8ybZ5ajjsmbVYi?filename=iOV7cYR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiOV7cYR.jpg&h=ccfd9db9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#東TOUCH"}]}